
           ----- CONTROL COMMANDS -----

  P  page status                 U  underline
  N  name the last error         O  overline
  V  view/hide character mods.   I  superscript
  F  format command display      K  subscript
  A  assistance                  B  boldface

  G  insert ghost hyphen

  W  delete word                 R  set a tab
  D  delete single character     T  move to tab
  X  delete line                 Y  clear a tab
